      },
      "date": "2013-10-16 09:12:25.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nWe have hit similar bug in own obdecho-survey testing. I that case i review that patch and may point to additional bug. IOCTL code take an obd via name2obd function and uses an obd_self_export to execute an operations.\nin that case clearing self_export to early will provide an access to freed pointer /un current patch/ or null pointer dereference.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "5fb705d528067d224b1c29c7c67cb101e23c3cdf",
