        "email": "nozaki.hiroya@jp.fujitsu.com",
        "username": "HiroyaNozaki"
      },
      "date": "2013-10-17 06:49:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nHi, Alexey.\nI quite agree with you. Actually I've discussed the similar problem you mentioned in LU-2603 ... thougth I couldn't do anything these days. Because, you know, class_name2obd(), class_uuid2obd() and something like them are a kind of lustre's infrustructre. so I'm a bit afraid of touching this things and it may need lots of time.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 7
    },
